instruction: Retrieve galaxies that are likely AGN hosts based on color (g-r > 1.03) and concentration index > 2.35, with redshift less than 0.141.
output: SELECT p.objID, p.ra, p.dec, s.z AS redshift, p.u, p.g, p.r, p.i, p.z, p.petroR50_r, p.petroR90_r, (p.petroR90_r/p.petroR50_r) AS concentration, p.err_u, p.err_g, p.err_r, p.err_i, p.err_z FROM SpecObj AS s JOIN PhotoObj AS p ON s.bestObjID = p.objID WHERE s.class = 'GALAXY' AND s.z < 0.141 AND (p.g - p.r) > 1.03 AND (p.petroR90_r/p.petroR50_r) > 2.35

instruction: Find galaxies in a rectangular region from RA=153.3182 to 154.1392 and DEC=-4.2264 to -3.8214, with redshift < 0.123 and g - r > 0.74.
output:
SELECT p.objID, p.ra, p.dec, s.z AS redshift, p.u, p.g, p.r, p.i, p.z, p.err_u, p.err_g, p.err_r, p.err_i, p.err_z FROM PhotoObj AS p
JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestObjID = p.objID
WHERE s.class = 'GALAXY' AND s.z < 0.123
AND (p.g - p.r) > 0.74

instruction: Show 100 galaxies with z > 0.02 and low magnitude errors (< 0.05)
output: SELECT p.objID, p.ra, p.dec, s.z AS redshift, p.u, p.g, p.r, p.i, p.z, p.err_u, p.err_g, p.err_r, p.err_i, p.err_z FROM SpecObj AS s JOIN PhotoObj AS p ON s.bestObjID = p.objID WHERE s.z > 0.02 AND p.err_u < 0.05 AND p.err_g < 0.05 AND p.err_r < 0.05 AND p.err_i < 0.05 AND p.err_z < 0.05

instruction: Find galaxies with R90/R50 greater than 2.6 and redshift < 0.2
output: SELECT p.objID, p.ra, p.dec, s.z AS redshift, p.u, p.g, p.r, p.i, p.z, p.petroR90_r, p.petroR50_r FROM SpecObj AS s JOIN PhotoObj AS p ON s.bestObjID = p.objID WHERE s.z < 0.2 AND (p.petroR90_r / p.petroR50_r) > 2.6

instruction: Select galaxies with g-r color > 0.6, r < 17, and no SATURATED flag
output: SELECT p.objID, p.ra, p.dec, s.z AS redshift, p.u, p.g, p.r, p.i, p.z FROM PhotoObj AS p JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestObjID = p.objID WHERE (p.g - p.r) > 0.6 AND p.r < 17 AND (p.flags & dbo.fPhotoFlags('SATURATED')) = 0

instruction: Find AGN galaxies with redshift between 0.107 and 0.248
output: SELECT p.objID, p.ra, p.dec, s.z AS redshift, p.u, p.g, p.r, p.i, p.z FROM PhotoObj AS p JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestObjID = p.objID WHERE (s.subClass = 'AGN' OR s.subClass = 'BROADLINE') AND s.z BETWEEN 0.107 AND 0.248
